data.description: You are going to love your new home in Yowell Ranch with easy access to the trail that leads to multiple parks within easy walking distance. With four bedrooms, an office, and a loft, your whole family will be able to spread out and find their own space. The home features an open floor plan that will make you feel very comfortable. The downstairs hardwood floors are a welcome sight upon entry into the house. The kitchen is beautifully laid out, spacious, with great features. The neighborhood has many amenities, plus the home is close to many more amenities, such as shopping, larger parks, and entertainment. The kids (even the grown ones) will love the upstairs loft. With the laundry room upstairs, there will be no hauling laundry up and down stairs. You will also enjoy privacy with the green belt directly behind the home as you relax on the extended back patio. Getting to the basketball courts, playgrounds, and the community pool is as easy as walking out your back gate. You've got to see this welcoming neighborhood and home.
